  <description><![CDATA[<p>Built into the cliff side, the VOI Grand Hotel Atlantis Bay is in the heart of Taormina Mare on the <span>Baia delle Sirene. </span>This unique hotel has terraces that descend towards the sea. Right on the edge of the bay you'll reach the swimming pool, with its large sun deck where you can relax under the shade of a parasol whilst enjoying a cool drink from the Dioniso Bar. The hotel's Ippocampo Restaurant has a lovely terrace where you can enjoy delicious gourmet cuisine whilst taking in the panoramic views of the bay. The hotel is a luxurious oasis of rest and relaxation with a wellness centre where you'll have a choice of treatments and massages (payable locally). The beautiful bedrooms are all individually decorated and all have a balcony or terrace with sea views. The cable car up to <a data-udi="umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6}" title="Taormina Area">Taormina</a> old town is just a short walk away, where you can explore the historic sights of the buzzing town. The location is a great base for exploring the region with Catania, Siracusa and <em>Mount Etna</em> within easy reach by car.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour by private car from Catania Airport </p>]]></description>
