  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Sea View Rooms</strong> are are about 18m² and sleep up to two adults. They are elegantly furnished have a balcony or terrace with sea view, air conditioning, television, minibar, safe, hairdryer, bathrobe and slippers.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 25-28m² and they can accommodate up to three adults or two adults and one child. The rooms overlook the beautiful waters of the bay. They have a large sitting room and bathrooms with a double marble sink. These rooms also have a coffee machine. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
